# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:11
translate french micha7a_be31aa9e:

    # "I spend some time talking to Gertrude about the things that have been on my mind. Then when I am about to leave and head to class, she stops me."
    "Je passe un moment à parler à Gertrude de ce qui me trotte dans la tête. Puis, alors que je m’apprête à partir pour aller en cours, elle m’arrête."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:12
translate french micha7a_039a0a46:

    # sc "Hey, before you leave, I wanted to tell you that I talked to Mi-Cha about you."
    sc "Hé, avant que tu partes, je voulais te dire que j’ai parlé de toi à Mi-Cha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:13
translate french micha7a_ae871f39:

    # pc "Oh yeah?"
    pc "Ah oui ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:14
translate french micha7a_13380f5e:

    # sc "She's very shy, but I talked her into having a little coffee meet-up with you. Can you meet her this evening?"
    sc "Elle est très timide, mais je l’ai convaincue de prendre un café avec toi. Tu peux la voir ce soir ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:18
translate french micha7a_5ec9bea1:

    # sc "Great! I'll let her know to meet you in the school café this evening."
    sc "Super ! Je lui dirai de te retrouver au café de l’école ce soir."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:19
translate french micha7a_a8af18a8:

    # pc "Cool, I'm looking forward to it."
    pc "Cool, j’ai hâte."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:20
translate french micha7a_e4769446:

    # sc "Okay, I'll see you later, [pcname]."
    sc "D'accord, à tout à l'heure, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:23
translate french micha7a_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "À tout à l'heure..."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:29
translate french micha7a_6750acb1:

    # sc "Oh, I'm sorry. I thought you were."
    sc "Oh, désolée. Je croyais que tu l'étais."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:30
translate french micha7a_9f1153c2:

    # sc "Okay then. She'll be disappointed, but I'll let her know."
    sc "Bon, d'accord. Elle va être déçue, mais je lui ferai savoir."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:31
translate french micha7a_9c57fd84:

    # sc "I'll see you later, [pcname]."
    sc "À tout à l'heure, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:39
translate french micha7_617439f0:

    # "I head over to the café for my coffee date with Mi-Cha."
    "Je me dirige vers la cafétéria pour mon rendez-vous avec Mi-Cha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:44
translate french micha7_046f6d25:

    # "When I walk into the café, I spot Mi-Cha sitting alone at one of the tables. She sees me immediately, as if she has been staring at the door waiting for me to enter."
    "Quand j'entre dans le café, j'aperçois Mi-Cha assise seule à l'une des tables. Elle me voit immédiatement, comme si elle avait les yeux rivés sur la porte en attendant que j'entre."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:47
translate french micha7_715a3be9:

    # "She immediately stands and walks up towards me."
    "Elle se lève aussitôt et s'avance vers moi."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:49
translate french micha7_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/micha_7_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_7_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:50
translate french micha7_b81c6f86:

    # mc "Hello, [pcname]. My name is Mi-Cha. It is very nice to meet you."
    mc "Bonjour, [pcname]. Je m'appelle Mi-Cha. Je suis ravie de te rencontrer."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:51
translate french micha7_65b65cd2:

    # pc "Hi, Mi-Cha. We've met already in the lobby remember?"
    pc "Salut, Mi-Cha. On s'est déjà rencontrés dans le hall, tu te souviens ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:53
translate french micha7_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/micha_yes1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_yes1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:54
translate french micha7_076877b6:

    # mc "Yes, I remember."
    mc "Oui, je m'en souviens."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:55
translate french micha7_1d573332:

    # pc "Do you want a coffee?"
    pc "Tu veux un café ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:57
translate french micha7_bf8efb1f:

    # "She doesn't say anything in response, instead just nodding her head slightly."
    "Elle ne répond pas, se contentant de hocher légèrement la tête."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:60
translate french micha7_b6487666:

    # bn "Hi there. What can I get for you?"
    bn "Bonjour. Que puis-je te servir ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:61
translate french micha7_fa4d4666:

    # pc "What would you like, Mi-Cha? I'll pay. Anything you want."
    pc "Qu'est-ce que tu veux, Mi-Cha ? C'est moi qui paie. Tout ce que tu veux."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:62
translate french micha7_816eccbd:

    # mc "You first, please."
    mc "Toi d'abord, s'il te plaît."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:63
translate french micha7_c24a94ff:

    # pc "Okay. I'll have a hot vanilla latte."
    pc "D'accord. Je vais prendre un latte chaud à la vanille."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:64
translate french micha7_0515f2bf:

    # mc "I will have the same."
    mc "Je vais prendre la même chose."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:65
translate french micha7_a4c27a52:

    # bn "Sure thing. Two hot vanilla lattes coming right up."
    bn "Bien sûr. Deux lattes chauds à la vanille, ça arrive tout de suite."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:68
translate french micha7_9e1b5b12:

    # "We wait for our drinks, I pay, then we go to a table and sit down."
    "On attend nos boissons, je paie, puis on va s'asseoir à une table."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:69
translate french micha7_c8eefb91:

    # "Mi-Cha doesn't say anything, just looking down at her coffee and smiling nervously."
    "Mi-Cha ne dit rien, elle regarde juste son café et sourit nerveusement."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:74
translate french micha7_2aebf130:

    # mc "Very good, thank you."
    mc "Très bon, merci."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:80
translate french micha7_2aebf130_1:

    # mc "Very good, thank you."
    mc "Très bon, merci."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:83
translate french micha7_fa75bbc3:

    # pc "Are you okay?"
    pc "Ça va ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:84
translate french micha7_dc52a31e:

    # pc "You seem a little nervous."
    pc "Tu as l'air un peu nerveuse."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:86
translate french micha7_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/micha_yes2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_yes2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:87
translate french micha7_d1bf83b5:

    # mc "Yes. I am."
    mc "Oui. Je le suis."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:88
translate french micha7_fb27d9a1:

    # pc "You don't have to be nervous around me. I'm not going to hurt you."
    pc "Tu n'as pas à être nerveuse avec moi. Je ne vais pas te faire de mal."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:89
translate french micha7_27577933:

    # mc "I know. I really want you to like me."
    mc "Je sais. J'ai vraiment envie que tu m'apprécies."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:90
translate french micha7_fcf5ae2f:

    # pc "I do like you."
    pc "Je t'apprécie."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:93
translate french micha7_81709362:

    # mc "You do?"
    mc "Vraiment ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:94
translate french micha7_423fa223:

    # pc "Sure. That's why I asked Gertrude to set up this date."
    pc "Bien sûr. C'est pour ça que j'ai demandé à Gertrude d'organiser ce rendez-vous."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:95
translate french micha7_6af12bd8:

    # mc "This is a date?"
    mc "C'est un rendez-vous ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:96
translate french micha7_c1f89784:

    # pc "A coffee date, yeah."
    pc "Un rendez-vous autour d'un café, oui."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:99
translate french micha7_57067727:

    # mc "Not the kind of date that ends in bed though?"
    mc "Mais pas le genre de rendez-vous qui finit au lit ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:102
translate french micha7_7d70b936:

    # mc "Good. I do not think I am ready for that yet."
    mc "Tant mieux. Je ne pense pas être encore prête pour ça."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:104
translate french micha7_8d1c80ad:

    # mc "No!"
    mc "Non !"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:105
translate french micha7_8413dde0:

    # mc "I'm sorry. I do not think I am ready for that yet."
    mc "Je suis désolée. Je ne pense pas être encore prête pour ça."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:108
translate french micha7_7d63d9da:

    # mc "I am very sorry. Did I offend you?"
    mc "Je suis vraiment désolé. Je t'ai offensée ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:109
translate french micha7_8b131ed8:

    # mc "I did not mean I would not want to go to bed with you. But I feel uncomfortable about it right now."
    mc "Je ne voulais pas dire que je ne voudrais pas coucher avec toi. Mais ça me met mal à l'aise pour le moment."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:110
translate french micha7_0d2c9d39:

    # pc "It's okay, I wasn't suggesting that. You didn't offend me."
    pc "Ce n'est pas grave, je ne suggérais pas ça. Tu ne m'as pas offensée."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:113
translate french micha7_0e8b4e1b:

    # mc "Oh no, I am making things worse aren't I?"
    mc "Oh non, je ne fais qu'empirer les choses, n'est-ce pas ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:114
translate french micha7_c767c9ce:

    # mc "I am so bad at this."
    mc "Je suis vraiment nul dans ce domaine."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:115
translate french micha7_c1e312a1:

    # pc "It's okay, really. Just calm down."
    pc "Ce n'est pas grave, vraiment. Calme-toi."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:118
translate french micha7_87a0b25e:

    # "I reach over and place my hand over hers. She starts to pull away at first, then relaxes."
    "Je tends la main et la pose sur la sienne. Elle commence par se reculer, puis se détend."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:121
translate french micha7_7c1c3cc4:

    # mc "Miss Spann did not tell me that you asked for this date. I thought that she set it up because she wanted me to meet people."
    mc "Mlle Spann ne m’a pas dit que c’était toi qui avais demandé ce rendez-vous. Je pensais qu’elle l’avait organisé parce qu’elle voulait que je fasse des rencontres."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:122
translate french micha7_36fab42e:

    # mc "It does make me feel better that you requested it."
    mc "Ça me rassure de savoir que c’est toi qui l’as demandé."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:123
translate french micha7_f3c20824:

    # mc "Why did you want to buy me coffee?"
    mc "Pourquoi tu as voulu m’offrir un café ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:124
translate french micha7_f0ffbaf0:

    # pc "I don't know. I thought you were cute and could use a friend."
    pc "Je sais pas. Je te trouvais mignonne et je me suis dit que t’avais besoin d’un ami."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:127
translate french micha7_41d2c325:

    # mc "You think that I am cute?"
    mc "Tu me trouves mignonne ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:128
translate french micha7_d54e19e4:

    # pc "Yeah. You're very cute."
    pc "Oui. Tu es très mignonne."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:132
translate french micha7_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:133
translate french micha7_5b61e929:

    # mc "Thank you, [pcname]."
    mc "Merci, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:134
translate french micha7_61a02886:

    # mc "I… think that you are cute as well."
    mc "Je… je te trouve mignonne aussi."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:137
translate french micha7_3b1b3410:

    # mc "Oh no, I should not have said that. I can't believe I said that."
    mc "Oh non, je n’aurais pas dû dire ça. Je n’arrive pas à croire que j’ai dit ça."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:138
translate french micha7_84587f43:

    # pc "What? It's okay that you think I'm cute."
    pc "Quoi ? Ça ne fait rien si tu me trouves mignonne."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:139
translate french micha7_a67a4bd1:

    # mc "No. I can't. I should go."
    mc "Non. Je ne peux pas. Je devrais y aller."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:140
translate french micha7_59ee5f3a:

    # pc "Why? You've barely drunk your coffee. I'd like to talk to you more."
    pc "Pourquoi ? Tu as à peine bu ton café. J’aimerais bien continuer à discuter avec toi."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:142
translate french micha7_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/micha_imsorry2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_imsorry2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:143
translate french micha7_918fea83:

    # mc "I'm sorry."
    mc "Je suis désolée."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:146
translate french micha7_6305b1a7:

    # mc "Is it okay if I leave?"
    mc "Ça te dérange si je pars ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:151
translate french micha7_d7eacc92:

    # mc "I know better than to be so forward."
    mc "Je sais bien qu’il ne faut pas être aussi directe."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:152
translate french micha7_cafb4599:

    # mc "I have been taught better than to say things like that."
    mc "On m’a appris à ne pas dire des choses comme ça."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:153
translate french micha7_f3946300:

    # mc "I am very sorry, but I would like to go now."
    mc "Je suis vraiment désolée, mais j’aimerais partir maintenant."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:157
translate french micha7_bb0eeaf4:

    # mc "Thank you."
    mc "Merci."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:158
translate french micha7_c5f761de:

    # mc "I'm very sorry."
    mc "Je suis vraiment désolée."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:161
translate french micha7_3ac8722a:

    # pc "There's no reason to apologize. You haven't done anything wrong."
    pc "Tu n’as aucune raison de t’excuser. Tu n’as rien fait de mal."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:163
translate french micha7_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/micha_thankyou1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:164
translate french micha7_024933de:

    # mc "Thank you. You're very kind."
    mc "Merci. Tu es très gentil."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:165
translate french micha7_26dc8eb0:

    # pc "Can we at least try this again sometime?"
    pc "On peut au moins réessayer un jour ?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:168
translate french micha7_d6451512:

    # "She makes a squeaking sound somewhere deep in her throat, as if the words are being forcefully pushed out."
    "Elle émet un petit cri au fond de la gorge, comme si les mots étaient expulsés de force."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:169
translate french micha7_f800bed0:

    # mc "Yes."
    mc "Oui."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:172
translate french micha7_f5c4b536:

    # "Then she practically runs out of the café."
    "Puis elle sort pratiquement en courant du café."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:175
translate french micha7_b95ac3d7:

    # "Well that was definitely one of the weirder first dates I've had. Not sure what was going on with her."
    "Eh bien, c'était sans aucun doute l'un des premiers rendez-vous les plus bizarres que j'ai eus. Je ne sais pas trop ce qui lui arrivait."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:176
translate french micha7_9788c24f:

    # "But she did say yes to another date."
    "Mais elle a accepté un autre rendez-vous."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha7.rpy:179
translate french micha7_2b06c7c2:

    # "Maybe that one will go a little more smoothly."
    "Peut-être que celui-là se passera un peu mieux."

